{"tid":1536774,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"嬲>圍差館>送頭>好嬲>圍差館>送頭>勁嬲>圍差館>送頭>......","createTime":"2019-09-03T17:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T17:33:38.000Z","uid":122386,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c625f4201cf927b82b3ef11af7ba0e18bbcdc565","tid":1536774,"uid":122386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:14:00.000Z","msg":"搞咗咁多次，搞咗啲咩花樣? 明知死路一條，次次攞laser pointer照幾照，鳩叫一輪就比人趕，比人打，比人捉<br />\n<br />\n比人捉咗，更多人嬲，點知都係做同一樣嘢，同一結局<br />\n如果你好嬲，想鳩叫一輪發洩，不如去海邊叫喇，效果一樣架，對家都係不痛不癢，仲唔洗益ot比佢地<br />\n<br />\n而家已經係消耗戰，對家無限同志們，尼邊拉一個少一個，請大家謀定而後動，諗清楚下一步，控制唔到自己怒火唔單只害己，更加會害人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31d0443997fde5e47c0f673cb282913a3407a939","tid":1536774,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:14:54.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主